This Park is abut four and a half months old beautiful park in Peoria, Park has a shaded play area for the kids & shaded water park, Grass area shaded picnic and barbecue areas, it's a  great park also nice clean new restrooms, Parking lot is well lit at night.
Even the play area is well lit for the evening, It seems to get kind of busy in the late afternoons, Park also has a stage area so you can have a puppet show or whatever you want to do, I highly recommend to come and check out the park the city of Peoria has done very good job keeping this park nice and clean.
A fun place for families and children.

