This park has everything!
There is a nice little lake for fishing that has a fountain  in the middle.
The playground is covered for shade, and there are tree basic areas to it.
One area is for kids between 2 and 5, another is for 5 to 8, and there is an area for bigger kids as well.
They have a large baseball field area with multiple  fields.
This park also has large open grass area so kids can just run around as well.
The highlight of this park is their splash pad area!
It is a really cool set up and a larger then normal area for the kids to play.
Bring a towel and try to joy the Arizona summer.
Good job City of Peoria.

